
1 -  run node -v
2 - if your node version is inferior to v0.10.40 download the .pkg from here https://nodejs.org/download/release/latest-v0.10.x/
.
3 - close studio if you have it opened .
4 - Install the node package
5 - shutdown mac
6 - power on mac
7 -  run the following commands 
    > sudo npm i -g appcelerator
    > appc setup
